longInfo:
Passport required.
- Passports and other documents accepted for entry must be
  valid on arrival. 
Passport Exemptions:
- Holders of emergency or temporary passports.

VISA NOT REQUIRED.

Additional Information:
- All visitors are required to have health insurance which can
  be purchased on arrival in Minsk (MSQ). 
Warning:
- Nationals of Uzbekistan are required to hold a biometric
  passport when departing Uzbekistan
